{"tid":1175752,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"LP6加推143伙 售價510萬起","createTime":"2019-05-28T18:25:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T17:23:21.000Z","uid":256095,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"b571872e31cf03a25b58cc12978ca7f268b99795","tid":1175752,"uid":256095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T18:25:10.000Z","msg":"南豐集團旗下將軍澳日出康城LP6加推第6號價單，涉及143個單位，包括25個一房戶、45個兩房戶、23個三房戶、41個四房戶和9個五房戶。<br />\n<br />\n扣除最高18.58%折扣優惠後，該批單位折實售價由510萬至5987萬元，呎價13595元至23487元，當中包括頂層特式單位及極高層大單位樓王，整批單位平均呎價約18161元。<br />\n<br />\n同時，今天公布最新銷售安排及已上載至物業網站，本周六(6月1日)以先到先得形式發售100個單位。<br />\n<br />\nLP6迄今累售2236伙，佔項目總伙數約93%，套現約181億元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果想買600萬以下一房有無機？<br />\n要幾時去排隊？ 使唔使排通宵...<br />\n之前抽montara抽唔到<br />\n好想買康城一房<br />\n求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08f2f9d602704b564bccaa599fe0f25764e02cec","tid":1175752,"uid":255931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T18:50:41.000Z","msg":"11點開門交FILE指明想要嘅嗰間單位，到時應該都幾十檯去吼住啲一房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果有多過一檯要嗰間單位，就即場抽籤（抽波仔）"},{"pid":"3fff9ffc1ca23b7f0b84a46175e9b93971b76e02","tid":1175752,"uid":255931,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T19:13:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R5FVfHZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR5FVfHZ.jpg&h=bb8dda85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n疊埋心水等7/6禮拜五 MONTARA 2B 好過啦<br />\n而家全香港都啄住600萬以下嚟追，二手得返大埔大圍都唔太多盤"},{"pid":"a5acc9d4b64a644579502a025b01dc2988419667","tid":1175752,"uid":256095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"08f2f9d602704b564bccaa599fe0f25764e02cec","tid":1175752,"uid":255931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T18:50:41.000Z",